columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model.

columns.name: creation_time
columns.description: A timestamp that indicates when the model was created.

columns.name: enable_network_isolation
columns.description: If True, no inbound or outbound network calls can be made to or from the model container.

columns.name: execution_role_arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role that you specified for the model.

columns.name: containers
columns.description: The containers in the inference pipeline.

columns.name: inference_execution_config
columns.description: Specifies details of how containers in a multi-container endpoint are called.

columns.name: primary_container
columns.description: The location of the primary inference code, associated artifacts, and custom environment map that the inference code uses when it is deployed in production.

columns.name: vpc_config
columns.description: A VpcConfig object that specifies the VPC that this model has access to.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: The list of tags for the model.
